Untar the latest kernel-source
cd [kernel source dir]
patch -p1 < [hrtime patch for given kernel version]

During the configuration process,
enable
'Prompt for development and/or incomplete code/drivers' (CONFIG_EXPIREMENTAL)
and 
'High-resolution process virtual time support (NEW)' (CONFIG_HRTIME)
and optionally
'High-resolution process utime/stime support (NEW)' (CONFIG_HRUSTIME)
